  <ul>
    <li>CBD A-grade and B-grade office towers</li>
    <li>Commercial precincts and mixed-use developments</li>
    <li>Strata-titled commercial buildings</li>
    <li>Corporate campuses and business parks</li>
    <li>Professional services buildings</li>
    <li>Government leased commercial premises</li>
  </ul>

