  <h2>Risks and Compliance Requirements</h2>
  <p>Key risks in office tower cleaning include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Inconsistent delivery across large floor plates generating tenant complaints</li>
    <li>Security breaches through inadequate key control and access management</li>
    <li>Chemical management issues in occupied or partially-occupied buildings</li>
    <li>Performance failures that affect tenant satisfaction scores and renewal decisions</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    After-hours access management is a significant security and liability consideration for building owners and strata managers. All access procedures must be formally documented and approved before cleaning commences.
  </p>

  <QuoteBlock
    quote="Digital audit tools provide building managers with more visibility into after-hours cleaning performance than supervised daytime cleaning typically delivers. Timestamps don't lie."
    attribution="CPC Commercial Operations"
